folder: Lincoln Avenue & South Railroad Avenue, Staten Island, NY
original_title: Richmond: Lincoln Avenue - South Railroad Avenue
text:
(1)
Lincoln Avenue, at the N.E. corner of South Railroad Avenue,
showing Semler's Midland Park Hotel. The view is east along
Lincoln Avenue, across the Staten Island Railroad grade crossing, as viewed from North Railroad Avenue.
May 26, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
(2)
The same, another view.
May 26, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
(3) An additional view.
May 26, 1935
P.L. Sperr.
